<D>__{sit.}
<A>__{the students sit once again as mr. nolan walks to the front of the room.}
<C>__{mr. nolan}
<D>__{i will be teaching this class through exams. we'll find a permanent english teacher during the break. who will tell me where you are in the pritchard textbook?}
<C>__{mr. nolan}
<D>__{mr. anderson?}
<C>__{todd}
<D>__{uh, in the, in the pr }
