<D>__{all of you, down. i want you seated. do you hear me?}
<C>__{mr. nolan}
<D>__{sit down!}
<A>__{keating stands in the doorway, staring up at the boys in wonder. a smile comes to his face.}
<C>__{keating}
<D>__{thank you, boys. thank you.}
